title: 10 Amazing TV Shows You Wish You Knew Earlier!
author: TechGumbo
comment: What is your favorite TV show that you think more people should be watching? Over the last several years, there have been many great shows that have been cancelled due to lack of viewership. Like many people, I'm still hoping that Hannibal will come back. 🤐
I'm always glad when I find out about a show late.. because then I can binge watch the whole thing without having to wait a year or more between seasons!
" Person of Interest " was one of the best shows on TV.
The last kingdom definitely a hidden gem.
"border town" Finnish crime drama is really well made series.
description:
These are best TV shows that you may have missed. While there are so many great TV shows that get a lot of attention like Stranger Things, Westworld, and Game of Thrones, just to name a few. There are other amazing shows that deserve to have more viewers. In this video, I’ll show you 10 TV shows that you’ll wish you knew about earlier.
